question: What restaurant can I find within 170 kilometers from Gator Country Wildlife Adventure Park, Beaumont, TX towards Walter Hall Park, League City, TX?
sql:
WITH
    angle AS (SELECT degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-94.274211 29.929639)',4326)::geography, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-95.10298 29.513607)',4326)::geography)) AS value)
SELECT * FROM pois,angle
WHERE amenity = 'restaurant'
AND ST_DWithin(pois.geometry, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-94.274211 29.929639)',4326)::geography, 170000)
AND (degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-94.274211 29.929639)',4326)::geography, pois.geometry)) BETWEEN angle.value - 22.5 AND angle.value + 22.5);
